                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 183va: This is a book which Wälättä Gäbrǝʾel has donated to the [fol. 183vb] church of Maryam (in) Fäqada so that it may be for her a guide in the Kingdom of Heaven. He who steals it or erases (its text) shall be excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.</q>
                           The letter ቃ in ወዘፈሐቃ፡ is written with a horizontal upper stroke characteristic of the letter for the spirantized ejective velar in Tǝgrǝñña.
